title: Car & Driver Magazine. December 2010.
description:
Car & Driver Magazine. December 2010.

Car and Driver is the most widely-read automotive magazine, 
and for good reason. Each issue comes jam-packed with detailed 
articles about the newest advances in automotive technology, 
exciting photography showcasing the hottest cars and profiles 
of the movers and shakers that make the motors run. Car and 
Driver is highly acclaimed for its automotive journalistic 
excellence.

Enjoy.
